Tests of REPL-specific functionality.

For things that are supposed to be different in the REPL and in files,
add one test to the repl*.isaw sequence and one to the file*.saw
sequence, WITH MATCHING NUMBERS.

Tests of things like REPL :-commands should be named something else.

Note that essentially everything in here must use test-and-diff
because the REPL traps errors: the exit status of SAW itself after an
unexpected failure in a *.isaw file will still be 0.
